{
  "stem": "2533.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And from that day on, we had to be in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, we-- we later on learned--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--after the Germans, you know, went away in the ghetto, we-- we couldn't go back to live at home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my parents, the father was with us, but my mother, grandmother, great grandmother, they come into to ghetto, and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kalb ?] found a family too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were living the ghetto, but the ghetto was very small.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took a couple of streets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they-- they-- they just divided things, and that's where you have to stay.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There wasn't many left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were only maybe about 700 people, and I don't know how many houses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, later on when it was a little bit eased up, and we were allowed to go because it was not far from the garden where we had, so we were allowed to sneak in and get something from the garden.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto, we had only one room and a kitchen and a little shed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we managed to, you know, to have some straw mattresses and all that at night time to put on the floor where to sleep and all that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So fuel was very scarce.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't know how my parents managed, but they managed somehow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The house, no-- the-- no, the family home, the [INAUDIBLE] took it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and they-- they had the secretaries stay there, and some offices was all for the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was dissolved straight away when the-- when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, that was-- everything was taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe he got something out of it, but I wasn't old enough to-- to inquire about things like that yet.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
